snippet.textDisplay:
And here's another Mind blowing creation.
Ofcourse! Mera dil hai Pakistani. Is yours too?
Well Well Well!
Am Saraiki Sindhi  and we people don't have capability of controlling our emotions and You know what? When that Ali Azmat's part started,I plugged my headphones  and Started Jhoomar(Sindhi Cultural Dance).😂😂😂😂😂😂😂😂😂😂😂 Coz the beats were same as the Dhol's beat we play in weddings.
Lots of love for Mangal ,Shayan ,Darehan and Ali Azmat.
You guys did a great job.
Am actually gonna play this song in My friends wedding for Jhoomar.😂😂😂😂😂😂😂😂😂 It will be fun.
